{"id": 1992, "genre": 1000, "title": "你在什么情况下会“特别注重品牌出身”？", "description": "国产的还是进口的？阳澄湖大闸蟹还是大湖蟹？你真的会介意什么？(题图来自：Pixabay)", "record_count": 6891, "comment_count": 27, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171105142050r9EUg5ptTZmI0CzW.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-06T17:00:35Z", "questions": [{"id": 3234, "title": "你在什么情况下会“特别注重品牌出身”？", "content": "你在什么情况下会特别“注重品牌出身”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 246483, "content": "自己还好，给小孩买吃的用的，会尤其对产地和品质有要求", "image": "img/option/option/20171105160212bjOEAJBZ1vidGx2q.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 246484, "content": "名声在外的消费品，会注重出身，像是茶、咖啡、酒", "image": "img/option/option/20171105154455T6FBzdserufR3DwY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 246485, "content": "不同产地的版本的配方和成分不一样的产品，例如日版、台版、美版不同的护肤品", "image": "img/option/option/20171105155939zLF3cnCmeyMd6gTJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 246487, "content": "不同产地的版本的款型、面料、价格不一样的产品，比如衣服和鞋，会看看made in 哪里", "image": "img/option/option/20171105153643TQuapw4yrAFzREDv.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 246486, "content": "选需要技术含量的制造品会多留意产地，例如德国车、瑞士表…之类", "image": "img/option/option/201711051544319cbRUdhNnq4eu5Dy.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 246488, "content": "特别在乎功效和安全性的东西，比如买医疗保健品，会看是否国产", "image": "img/option/option/20171105154850hlwZrqMfCN2yez5E.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 246489, "content": "有原产地优势的农副产品，智利车厘子阳澄湖的蟹之类", "image": "img/option/option/20171105160129uFlt5Akzb4mWLDoJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}